WIMESSA invites you to the first official language-speaking session! 
Grab some tea, get comfy, and practice your Arabic in a friendly space! All proficiencies are welcome. !نراكم هناك

We invite you to our WIMESSA x MIISSC Grad Research Talk featuring two PhD students from the Institute of Islamic Studies! The talk will happen on Friday, November 8th beginning at 5:30 in the Morrice Hall Theatre. We look forward to this wonderful research showcase!
